two miles away.

01:24:53.853 --> 01:24:56.354
Hey, come on, let's go inside.

01:24:57.123 --> 01:24:58.591
Come with me.

01:24:59.492 --> 01:25:01.725
Stella, now's not the time
to be rebellious.

