No, no, no, no, no. No!

01:29:23.355 --> 01:29:24.356
Whew!

01:29:48.848 --> 01:29:49.849
Hey.

01:29:51.917 --> 01:29:53.219
Everything all right?

01:30:04.130 --> 01:30:05.164
Yeah.

01:30:09.335 --> 01:30:10.870
Yeah, I'm good.

01:30:14.440 --> 01:30:16.075
Oh!

