more blankets over here.

01:37:28.407 --> 01:37:30.442
Just breathe.
Stella?

01:37:30.677 --> 01:37:32.409
I've got you, honey.

01:37:32.411 --> 01:37:34.377
Stella?

01:37:34.379 --> 01:37:35.546
